* Total Revenue (V3): `=SUMIF($1$1:$ZZ$1,"TOTAL",$3$3:$ZZ$3)`
* Total GP (W3): `=SUMIF($1$1:$ZZ$1,"GP",$3$3:$ZZ$3)`

These formulas satisfy the requirement: they automatically sum all columns in row 3 whose header matches the category, and they will continue to work as columns are added.

